<SYNC Start=247616><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=248049><P Class=KRCC>
꾹!
<SYNC Start=249767><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=269524><P Class=KRCC>
그만해, 요 녀석…
<SYNC Start=271374><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=272021><P Class=KRCC>
